    • Class nl.rug.aoop.asteroids.model.gameobjects.GameObject extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • destroyed
          boolean destroyed
          A flag that is set when this object collides with another. This tells the game engine that this object should be removed from the game.
        • location
          Point2D.Double location
          An x and y value pair indicating the object's current location.
        • radius
          double radius
          Radius of the object.
        • stepsUntilCollisionPossible
          int stepsUntilCollisionPossible
          The number of game ticks that must pass before this object is allowed to collide with other game objects. This can also be thought of as a grace period, or temporary immunity.
        • velocity
          Point2D.Double velocity
          An x and y value pair indicating the object's current velocity, in pixels per game tick.
